HEADWORD: Norroy
<hw>Nor"roy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Lit., north king, fr.
F. <ets>nord</ets> north + <ets>roi</ets> king.]</ety> <fld>(Her.)</fld>
<def>The most northern of the English Kings-at-arms. See
<cref>King-at-arms</cref>, under <er>King</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
